{"tid":2401174,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【估國家】女員工到職1個月就被已婚主管嘿咻　開房間2小時中毒斃命","createTime":"2021-02-09T13:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T14:09:18.000Z","uid":24163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"eda618bc2b2823681552c14c0da1728c8c8cb84d","tid":2401174,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T13:46:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210209/XINW5EQPMFGPPOZ5WPRAQMHI4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210209%2FXINW5EQPMFGPPOZ5WPRAQMHI4I%2F&d=%2BlEHcpGCWp7P1IX%2BOWqMQqf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=a2902475\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210209%2FXINW5EQPMFGPPOZ5WPRAQMHI4I%2F&h=ad9cca7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210209/XINW5EQPMFGPPOZ5WPRAQMHI4I/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國廣東省佛山市一名23歲的陳姓女子，去年底到一家房地產公司任職後被已婚的主管看上，今年1月24日被主管帶去開房間做愛，豈料短短二、三個小時候，陳女竟然陳屍飯店房間內，檢方相驗指陳女是七氟烷（短時效吸入式麻醉藥）中毒身亡。警方目前立案調查，朝主管過失致死方向偵辦。<br />\n<br />\n據中國《澎湃新聞》報導，陳女家境不好，父母都是殘疾人士，父親已經離家多年未歸，她和哥哥靠著外祖父母和舅舅的援助才得以完成學業。陳女去年畢業後，於12月27日找到一家房地產公司的職務，結果到職不到1個月，就被已婚主管帶去開房間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEbfkbT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEbfkbT.png&h=45506479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n23歲女員工（左）畢業時與母親合照。翻攝自《澎湃新聞》<br />\n陳女的舅舅表示，今年1月23日，陳女被主管帶去吃消夜、唱歌、喝酒，隔天凌晨3時許，主管先去飯店開房間後，再帶陳女入住，清晨5時多主管離開向飯店人員說是去買早餐，大約5時30分返回時請飯店人員幫忙開門，不久就指陳女出事了。依據屍檢報告，陳女符合七氟烷中毒致急性呼吸、循環功能障礙而死。<br />\n<br />\n主管事後向警方坦承，自己已婚，當晚有與陳女發生性行為。至於為何陳女會中毒死亡，警方不願透露，只表示已經立案調查。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"91c1a5edc3a2b3ae126c1941d92775585b623bd9","tid":2401174,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:01:04.000Z","msg":"湯丸唔打機轉行開風化post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceea7dd8ee81d7facfbee19a843e4a43e6fa083b","tid":2401174,"uid":24163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91c1a5edc3a2b3ae126c1941d92775585b623bd9","tid":2401174,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:01:04.000Z","msg":"湯丸唔打機轉行開風化post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:04:49.000Z","msg":"屌依家限一粒鐘開三個POST，想轉行都唔得，好無癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa281266d013e4fbe47bcaeec623ae5b22e54ed","tid":2401174,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEbfkbT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEbfkbT.png&h=45506479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n23歲女員工（左）畢業時與母親合照。<br />\n<br />\n點解係幫個死者打格但就公開在身果個嘅樣嘅 未睇下面句嘢前我仲以為個先係23歲女員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6f55b504bd723be5b9029eb5d0b20cfd0cef6e1","tid":2401174,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efa281266d013e4fbe47bcaeec623ae5b22e54ed","tid":2401174,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEbfkbT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEbfkbT.png&h=45506479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n23歲女員工（左）畢業時與母親合照。<br />\n<br />\n點解係幫個死者打格但就公開在身果個嘅樣嘅 未睇下面句嘢前我仲以為個先係23歲女員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T14:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mEbfkbT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmEbfkbT.png&h=45506479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n23歲女員工（左）畢業時與母親合照。<br />\n<br />\n點解係幫個死者打格但就公開在生果個嘅樣嘅 未睇下面句嘢前我仲以為個老母先係23歲女員工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}